I"M<h2 id="ldpc-codes">LDPC Codes</h2>
<p>LDPC codes–(L)ow (D)ensity (P)arity (C)heck Codes–are codes which are defined by particularly sparse parity check matrices. The quality of being sparse is defined by an absurdly small ratio of 1s to 0s, as well as a large distribution uniformity of  1s within the parity check matrix.</p>

